<li><code class="directive"><a href="#allowoverride">AllowOverride</a></code></li>
<li><a href="../configuring.html">Fichiers de configuration</a></li>
<li><a href="../howto/htaccess.html">Fichiers .htaccess</a></li>
</ul>
